name: LocationPicker2
description: This is a fork of https://bitbucket.devops.nonprod.empf.local/scm/react/LocationPicker to make it accessible to Swift 4 Projects. LocationPickerViewController is a UIViewController subclass to let users choose locations by searching or selecting on map. It's designed to work as UIImagePickerController.
summary: UIViewController subclass for searching or selecting locations on map.
